## ⚠️ IMPORTANT: Deployment Requirements

This is a **full-stack application** and CANNOT run on Vercel or GitHub Pages.

### It CANNOT run:
❌ Node.js backend code
❌ tRPC procedures
❌ Database queries
❌ PayPal webhooks
❌ File uploads to S3

### Use these platforms for full-stack deployment:

| Platform | Frontend | Backend | Database | Cost |
|----------|----------|---------|----------|------|
| **Railway** | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ Included | Free tier available |
| **Render** | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ Included | Free tier available |
| **Manus** | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ Included | Production-ready |
| **Vercel** | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | Frontend only |
| **GitHub Pages** | ✅ Only | ❌ | ❌ | Frontend only |

### Recommended: Railway
Railway is the easiest for this full-stack app. It includes Node.js backend, database, and free tier.

See `RAILWAY_DEPLOYMENT.md` for setup instructions.
